Let's assume we want to test some functions from the `UserService` class. Open the `src/services/UserService.js` file and identify the functions you want to test.

For example, let's say we have a function `getUserById`:

```javascript
class UserService {
  constructor(userRepository) {
    this.userRepository = userRepository;
  }

  async getUserById(userId) {
    return await this.userRepository.findById(userId);
  }
}
